 bows would surely benefit from the str and dex here.<br><br>In any case, not meaning to open up one of those &quot;which class should get it threads&quot; just pointing out where it might have been most useful in our guild at our stage of equipping.  This is a nice piece for anyone who has the points of favor to get it though. Enjoy.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Bigskyn Biggerheart: <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=478057" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=478057</a></td></tr>
